PREAMBLE
This license grants you the right to view, download, study, and use the
source code and compiled artifacts of this project. It is a "source-available"
license and is not an open-source license: commercial exploitation of the
Software itself and standalone redistribution are not permitted.

DEFINITIONS
"The Software" means all modules and artifacts in this repository, including
pluginpulse-core, pluginpulse-companion, pluginpulse-hotreload,
pluginpulse-inject, and the in-browser web tool, in source and compiled form.
"Embedding" means including the Software inside a Minecraft plugin jar, either
by shading/relocating the pluginpulse-core library into a plugin at build time
as described in the documentation, or by injecting it into an existing plugin
jar with the web tool or pluginpulse-inject.

